r_k
\begin{cases} r       =& \frac{dV}{A}\\ \\ \vec{c} =& \frac{1}{A}\sum\limits_{k=1}^{d+1} A_k \vec{v}_k\\ \end{cases} \quad\text{ and }\quad \begin{cases} r_k     =& r\frac{A}{A-2A_k} = \frac{dV}{A - 2A_k}\\ \\ \vec{c}_k =& \frac{r_k}{r} \vec{c} + \left(1 - \frac{r_k}{r}\right) \vec{v}_k\\ \end{cases}
